<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">stakeholder</ENAMEX>) focus,


•
management control to employee empowerment,


•
reactive behavior to proactive approaches,


•
avoiding new technologies to embracing and leveraging
them,


•
hoarding knowledge to sharing knowledge,


•
avoiding risk to managing risk, and


•
protecting turf to forming <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">partnerships</ENAMEX>.


Leading public <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">organizations</ENAMEX> here in the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">United States</ENAMEX> and
